Golf Etc. Lakeland is owned and operated by the Millers,
golf enthusiasts who know exactly what it takes to fit your game. Not only have they been helping customers get the exact product they need, they have also been helping golfers all across Central Florida take strokes off their scores for the past 11 years.
Through their
Custom Fitting
process, JJ and Luke have consulted men and women on finding the products that perform better with their body types, unique swings, and styles of play. This experience and knowledge they provide will take your game to another level.
Luke Miller
Luke is a graduate from Lakeland Christian School and Florida Southern College in Lakeland. He enjoys spending time with his wife Cassie, and kids, Erin, Eli, Easton and Emelia.
JJ Miller
JJ coached golf at Southeastern University, using his experience to help build a powerful collegiate program. Outside of work he spends his time with his wife Cherie, and coaches his two boys', Jake and Nate, travel baseball team.
Jim Miller
Jim (Pap) brings business experience and financial balance, serving as the controller. He enjoys nothing more then spending time at Disney with his nine grandchildren.
